## C) Prompt & latency/cost trimming checklist

- [x] Compact prompt (remove redundancy; minimal system text)  
- [x] `max_tokens` capped to preserve completeness only  
- [x] Warmâ€‘up occurs at process start (`openai_wrapper.warmup()`)  
- [x] LRU embedding cache hits observed (>0% on repeated evals)  
- [x] Verify p50 â‰¤ 6.0s, p95 â‰¤ 9.0s after tuning

---

## D) Guardrails (enforced)

- **Strict JSON** with oneâ€‘shot formatâ€‘fix fallback; zero parse failures over stress (â‰¥200 calls).  
- **Abstain / lowâ€‘confidence**: if fused scores low/contradictory â†’ safe fallback with user advice.  
- **Evidence requirement**: on no evidence â†’ return `9999.99` + disclaimer (no hallucination).  
- **Policy wrappers**: perâ€‘request token caps & timeouts; userâ€‘facing disclaimer; internal debug id surfaced.
- **Stress run:** 7Ã— eval passes (~217 calls) on 2025-09-21 â†’ JSON parse failures **0/217**.

